description:
Anne`s classmate at college. Her coming from the same town as Anne`s deceased parents serves as a point of connection, and the two become good friends. With her good looks, money, and sense of humor, she stands out at the college, but she is indecisive. She is unable to decide whether to marry Alec or Alonzo. A resident of Patty`s Place. She grows up alongside Anne and her other friends.
Source: Official page
name: Philippa Gordon
